---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import PortfolioCTA from '../../components/PortfolioCTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Wedding Photography Case Study Anggie & Raden | Frame Of Rangga"
  description="Case study fotografi wedding Anggie & Raden concept, proses shoot, dan hasil final. Pendekatan cinematic storytelling untuk momen pernikahan yang berkesan."
  ogImage="https://for-portfolio-mu.vercel.app/assets/og/og-foto.jpg"
  ogUrl="https://for-portfolio-mu.vercel.app/case-study/wedding-anggie-raden"
>
  <Navbar slot="navbar" activePage="foto" />

  <!-- CASE STUDY HERO -->
  <section class="cs-hero" transition:animate="fade">
    <div class="cs-hero-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="cs-hero-inner">
      <div class="cs-hero-meta">
        <span class="cs-category-badge">Photography</span>
        <span class="cs-year">2024</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="cs-hero-title">Wedding Story:<br /><span class="cs-hero-accent">Anggie &amp; Raden</span></h1>
      <p class="cs-hero-sub">
        Bagaimana saya mengabadikan momen sakral pernikahan Anggie dan Raden dengan pendekatan cinematic portraiture yang autentik dan emosional.
      </p>
      <div class="cs-hero-stats">
        <div class="cs-stat">
          <span class="cs-stat-num">120+</span>
          <span class="cs-stat-label">Photos Delivered</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-stat">
          <span class="cs-stat-num">2</span>
          <span class="cs-stat-label">Shoot Sessions</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-stat">
          <span class="cs-stat-num">8</span>
          <span class="cs-stat-label">Jam Shooting</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-stat">
          <span class="cs-stat-num">100%</span>
          <span class="cs-stat-label">Client Satisfaction</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Hero Image -->
    <div class="cs-hero-image">
      <img
        src="/assets/foto/wedding/ultah raden 2 landscape.JPG"
        alt="Wedding Photography Anggie & Raden"
        loading="eager"
        fetchpriority="high"
      />
      <div class="cs-hero-image-overlay"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DIVIDER -->
  <div class="section-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- OVERVIEW -->
  <section class="cs-section cs-overview" transition:animate="fade">
    <div class="cs-inner">
      <div class="cs-overview-grid">
        <div class="cs-overview-left fade-up">
          <span class="cs-section-label gradient-label">OVERVIEW</span>
          <h2 class="cs-section-title">Tantangan &amp; Brief</h2>
          <p>
            Klien menginginkan dokumentasi pernikahan yang tidak hanya sekadar "foto seremonial" mereka ingin hasil yang mencerminkan emosi dan hubungan mereka secara autentik. Tantangan utama: mengelola waktu shoot yang terbatas sambil tetap menangkap momen-momen natural yang spontan.
          </p>
          <p>
            Sebagai seorang visual storyteller, fokus saya bukan hanya pada technical execution, tapi pada kemampuan membaca momen kapan harus interfere, kapan harus disappear dan biarkan momen mengalir natural.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-overview-right fade-up">
          <div class="cs-info-card">
            <div class="cs-info-row">
              <span class="cs-info-label">Client</span>
              <span class="cs-info-value">Anggie & Raden</span>
            </div>
            <div class="cs-info-row">
              <span class="cs-info-label">Kategori</span>
              <span class="cs-info-value">Wedding Photography</span>
            </div>
            <div class="cs-info-row">
              <span class="cs-info-label">Lokasi</span>
              <span class="cs-info-value">Depok, Jawa Barat</span>
            </div>
            <div class="cs-info-row">
              <span class="cs-info-label">Durasi</span>
              <span class="cs-info-value">2 Sessions, 8 Jam</span>
            </div>
            <div class="cs-info-row">
              <span class="cs-info-label">Services</span>
              <span class="cs-info-value">Pre-wedding &amp; Wedding Day</span>
            </div>
            <div class="cs-info-row">
              <span class="cs-info-label">Deliverables</span>
              <span class="cs-info-value">120+ Edited Photos, Online Gallery</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DIVIDER -->
  <div class="section-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- APPROACH -->
  <section class="cs-section cs-approach" transition:animate="fade">
    <div class="cs-inner">
      <div class="cs-approach-header fade-up">
        <span class="cs-section-label gradient-label">APPROACH</span>
        <h2 class="cs-section-title">Creative Direction</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-approach-grid fade-up">

        <div class="cs-approach-card">
          <div class="cs-approach-num">01</div>
          <h3>Pre-Production</h3>
          <p>
            Scouting lokasi terlebih dahulu untuk memahami cahaya natural dan composition points. Diskusi dengan klien untuk memahami dynamic pasangan bagaimana mereka berinteraksi, apa momen yang paling berarti bagi mereka.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="cs-approach-card">
          <div class="cs-approach-num">02</div>
          <h3>Cinematic Framing</h3>
          <p>
            Saya menghindari "pose standar pre-wedding" yang terasa fake. Sebagai gantinya, saya mengarahkan couples ke aktivitas natural jalan kaki, bercanda, melihat ke arah yang sama sambil saya wait and capture. Hasilnya: candid tapi tetap well-composed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="cs-approach-card">
          <div class="cs-approach-num">03</div>
          <h3>Natural Light Mastery</h3>
          <p>
            Golden hour adalah sahabat Fotografi. Tapi saya tidak bergantung sepenuhnya padanya. Saya memanfaatkan semua kondisi cahaya backlight, window light, bahkan low-light indoor untuk menciptakan dimensi dan depth dalam setiap frame.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DIVIDER -->
  <div class="section-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- GALLERY SHOWCASE -->
  <section class="cs-section cs-gallery" transition:animate="fade">
    <div class="cs-inner">
      <div class="cs-gallery-header fade-up">
        <span class="cs-section-label gradient-label">SELECTED WORKS</span>
        <h2 class="cs-section-title">Final Results</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-gallery-grid fade-up">
        <div class="cs-gallery-item cs-gallery-item-featured">
          <img
            src="/assets/foto/wedding/ultah raden 2 landscape.JPG"
            alt="Wedding Raden Portrait"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="cs-gallery-caption">
            <span class="cs-gallery-cat">Featured</span>
            <p>Raden Cinematic Portrait</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-gallery-item">
          <img
            src="/assets/foto/wedding/anggie 1.jpg"
            alt="Wedding Anggie Portrait"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="cs-gallery-caption">
            <span class="cs-gallery-cat">Bride</span>
            <p>Anggie Editorial Portrait</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-gallery-item">
          <img
            src="/assets/foto/wedding/anggie 2 landscape.jpg"
            alt="Wedding Candid Moment"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="cs-gallery-caption">
            <span class="cs-gallery-cat">Couple</span>
            <p>Candid Moment Akad</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-gallery-item">
          <img
            src="/assets/foto/wedding/anggie 4 landscape.jpg"
            alt="Wedding Anggie Editorial"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="cs-gallery-caption">
            <span class="cs-gallery-cat">Detail</span>
            <p>Anggie Natural Light</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DIVIDER -->
  <div class="section-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- POST-PROCESSING -->
  <section class="cs-section cs-post" transition:animate="fade">
    <div class="cs-inner">
      <div class="cs-post-grid fade-up">
        <div class="cs-post-left">
          <span class="cs-section-label gradient-label">POST-PRODUCTION</span>
          <h2 class="cs-section-title">Editing Philosophy</h2>
          <p>
            Setiap foto melewati proses editing yang deliberate. Saya tidak menerapkan preset generik setiap image disesuaikan berdasarkan mood, lighting condition, dan emotional tone dari momen itu sendiri.
          </p>
          <p>
            Hasil akhir: warna kulit yang natural dan akurat, tone yang cinematic tapi tidak over-processed, dengan contrast yang memberikan dimension tanpa sacrifice detail di highlights dan shadows.
          </p>
          <div class="cs-tools">
            <span class="cs-tool-pill">Adobe Lightroom Classic</span>
            <span class="cs-tool-pill">Capture One Pro</span>
            <span class="cs-tool-pill">Exposure X7</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-post-right">
          <div class="cs-process-flow">
            <div class="cs-process-step">
              <i class="fas fa-image"></i>
              <div>
                <h4>Color Grading</h4>
                <p>Consistent tonal palette across all 120+ images. Film-inspired warm tones dengan subtle teal shadows.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cs-process-step">
              <i class="fas fa-sliders-h"></i>
              <div>
                <h4>Retouching</h4>
                <p>Skin retouching yang natural menghilangkan distractions tanpa mengubah structural features subjek.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cs-process-step">
              <i class="fas fa-crop"></i>
              <div>
                <h4>Curating</h4>
                <p>Memilih 120+ best shots dari 800+ raw images. Setiap pilihan didasarkan pada emotional impact dan technical quality.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DIVIDER -->
  <div class="section-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- RESULTS / TESTIMONIAL -->
  <section class="cs-section cs-result" transition:animate="fade">
    <div class="cs-inner">
      <div class="cs-result-card fade-up">
        <div class="cs-result-quote">
          <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i>
          <blockquote>
            Hasilnya luar biasa! Rangga tidak hanya Fotografi dia storyteller. Setiap foto menangkap emosi yang kami rasakan saat itu juga. Photos itu akan kami simpan seumur hidup.
          </blockquote>
          <div class="cs-result-author">
            <div class="cs-result-avatar">A</div>
            <div>
              <p class="cs-result-name">Anggie</p>
              <p class="cs-result-role">Client Wedding Photography</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-result-metrics fade-up">
        <div class="cs-metric">
          <span class="cs-metric-num">120+</span>
          <span class="cs-metric-label">Photos Delivered</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-metric">
          <span class="cs-metric-num">100%</span>
          <span class="cs-metric-label">Delivered on Time</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-metric">
          <span class="cs-metric-num">0</span>
          <span class="cs-metric-label">Revisions Needed</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-metric">
          <span class="cs-metric-num">3</span>
          <span class="cs-metric-label">Referrals Generated</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DIVIDER -->
  <div class="section-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- NEXT PROJECT CTA -->
  <PortfolioCTA />

  <!-- Footer -->
  <Footer slot="footer" variant="minimal" />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ===== HERO ===== */
  .cs-hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 120px 64px 0;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .cs-hero-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10%;
    right: -5%;
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(163, 166, 255, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(60px);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cs-hero-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .cs-hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .cs-category-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    background: rgba(163, 166, 255, 0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(163, 166, 255, 0.2);
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .cs-year {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .cs-hero-title {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 60px);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    color: var(--on-surface);
  }

  .cs-hero-accent {
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
  }

  .cs-hero-sub {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .cs-hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cs-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .cs-stat-num {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .cs-stat-label {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
  }

  /* Hero image */
  .cs-hero-image {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(163, 166, 255, 0.08);
    box-shadow: 0 32px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  .cs-hero-image img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .cs-hero-image-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(6, 14, 32, 0.4), transparent 60%);
  }

  /* ===== SECTIONS ===== */
  .cs-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
  }

  .cs-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 64px;
  }

  .cs-section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .gradient-label {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-primary), var(--accent-secondary));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .cs-section-title {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--on-surface);
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .section-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to right,
      transparent,
      rgba(163, 166, 255, 0.12) 20%,
      rgba(193, 128, 255, 0.12) 80%,
      transparent
    );
    margin: 0 64px;
  }

  /* ===== OVERVIEW ===== */
  .cs-overview-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .cs-overview-left p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .cs-info-card {
    background: var(--surface-container);
    border: 1px solid rgba(163, 166, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 28px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .cs-info-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(163, 166, 255, 0.06);
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .cs-info-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .cs-info-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .cs-info-value {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--on-surface);
    text-align: right;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }

  /* ===== APPROACH ===== */
  .cs-approach-header {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .cs-approach-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .cs-approach-card {
    background: var(--surface-container);
    border: 1px solid rgba(163, 166, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cs-approach-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(163, 166, 255, 0.18);
  }

  .cs-approach-num {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .cs-approach-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--on-surface);
  }

  .cs-approach-card p {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
  }

  /* ===== GALLERY ===== */
  .cs-gallery-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
    grid-auto-rows: 280px;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .cs-gallery-item {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cs-gallery-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .cs-gallery-item-featured {
    grid-column: span 8;
    grid-row: span 2;
  }

  .cs-gallery-item:not(.cs-gallery-item-featured) {
    grid-column: span 4;
  }

  .cs-gallery-item img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: transform 0.7s ease;
  }

  .cs-gallery-item:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.04);
  }

  .cs-gallery-caption {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(6, 14, 32, 0.9), transparent);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .cs-gallery-cat {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .cs-gallery-caption p {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
  }

  /* ===== POST-PROCESSING ===== */
  .cs-post-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .cs-post-left p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .cs-tools {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .cs-tool-pill {
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(163, 166, 255, 0.2);
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .cs-process-flow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    background: var(--surface-container);
    border: 1px solid rgba(163, 166, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cs-process-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(163, 166, 255, 0.06);
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cs-process-step:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .cs-process-step:hover {
    background: var(--surface-container-highest);
  }

  .cs-process-step > i {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(163, 166, 255, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .cs-process-step h4 {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--on-surface);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .cs-process-step p {
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
  }

  /* ===== RESULT ===== */
  .cs-result-card {
    background: var(--surface-container);
    border: 1px solid rgba(163, 166, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .cs-result-quote i {
    font-size: 32px;
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: block;
  }

  .cs-result-quote blockquote {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--on-surface);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .cs-result-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
